author: arkurth
msg: Cleaned up reclaim.pm. Removed unnecessary call to get_next_image_DataStructure() in process(). Removed a few instances of duplicate code which did the same thing as insert_reload_and_exit(). The sub now gets called.
Removed argument where switch_state() is called in reclaim.pm::insert_reload_and_exit() which sets log.ending to EOR. This was causing the correct log.ending value to be overwritten by EOR.
